The word, “Abia” is currently trending on the micro blogging platform, Twitter, after Nigerian politician, Femi Fani-Kayode (FFK), was spotted at the just concluded All Progressive Congress (APC) convention as a delegate of Abia State.
Recall that APC did their convention yesterday at the Federal Capital Territory, Abuja, as the likes of Yahaya Bello, Mala Buni, Nasir el-Rufia, FFK and other members of the APC were spotted at the convention.
However, following the just concluded APC convention, former minister of aviation, FFK, could be seen rocking one of the APCs outfit round his neck with the inscription, “Abia state delegate”.
However, following such revelation, Nigerians took to the micro blogging platform, Twitter, to react, as many expressed confusion with regards to FFK being an Abia State delegate at the APC convention.
Others however, praised the politician with different names while also thanking him for representing Abia state at the convention.
